# arrivalDate

**Interface Property**

The arrival date for the trip.

## Declaration

```swift
arrivalDate?: Date;
```

## Discussion

Specify either a [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/EtaRequestOptions/departureDate] or an `arrivalDate`, but don’t set both. If you send both values, MapKit JS logs a warning.
